  <!-- ── WARRANTY ── -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow-sub">Warranty context</p>
      <h2>Thermador dishwasher warranty, and post-warranty reality</h2>
      <p>Thermador dishwasher warranty is 2 years on major parts, 1 year on everything else. During the warranty window, call Thermador at <strong>1-800-735-4328</strong> for Factory-Certified dispatch at no parts cost.</p>
      <p>Most of our Thermador dishwasher calls are 5-to-10-year-old units well outside the warranty window. The BSH chassis is durable, wash pumps typically run 10–15 years before replacement, heating elements 8–12, control boards highly variable (3 years to 15+). When a post-warranty Thermador dishwasher fails, the repair-or-replace math usually favors repair: a $400–$600 repair on a $2,500 appliance is a clear win over replacement. We'll tell you honestly if the math flips the other way, occasional 15-year-old units with multiple cascading failures where replacement makes more sense.</p>
    </div>
